CLIP Ranked Artists

(Image-heavy page! Please wait for it to load)

Updated 8/11/2022 with new artists

Want to test an artist against CLIP? Now you can!

Below you'll find a list of artists, each of which has been run through OpenAI's CLIP. I generate a score for each, as well as find similar artists (by text prompt) as well as the best stylistic matches to the sample art.

Images from the web serve as representative examples of that artist's style, and are used in finding stylstic matches.

Renders were created with Prog Rock Stable using simply "stunning portrait" or "stunning landscape" followed with "by (artist name)

Note: After number 450 or so the quality of CLIP's response becomes questionable, so you may see some weird matches and scores. You may also notice the rendered samples start to look similar to others, which basically means the artist's name had very little impact on the outcome (another sign they are not well represented in the model).

Message me on Discord if there's an artist you want included, or if you notice any incorrect art examples.

Please consider supporting me on Patreon to help keep this page improving.
